Maintainer: PVE XPU Manager <pve-xpu@localhost>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 12)
Standards-Version: 4.5.1

Package: pve-xpu-manager
Architecture: all
Depends: pve-manager (>= 8.0), perl, libpve-common-perl, pciutils, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Intel XPU/GPU Manager for Proxmox VE
 Provides discovery, monitoring, and SR-IOV virtual function management
 for Intel discrete GPUs (Flex/ATS-M, Ponte Vecchio, Battlemage) in
 Proxmox VE. Includes a web UI tab, REST API, and boot persistence.
